<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
    Preview image for Recent Transactions Widget.

    This drawable is displayed in the widget picker when users browse available widgets.
    It provides a visual representation of what the widget looks like on the home screen.

    Size: 4x3 cells (250dp x 180dp minimum)
    Displays sample data: "Recent Transactions" with a list of 5 transactions showing
    merchant names, color-coded amounts (red for debits, green for credits), and dates

    Note: This is a simplified visual representation using shapes. The actual widget
    uses Glance composables with real text rendering and dynamic transaction data.
    This preview helps users identify the widget in the picker.

    See: RecentTransactionsWidget, recent_transactions_widget_info.xml
-->
